    <details><summary>Do you provide plumbing and electrical services in Brampton?</summary><p>Yes. Fateh Plumbing & Electric provides plumbing and electrical services from Brampton across nearby GTA communities for homeowners, landlords, restaurants, retail units, small businesses and property managers.</p></details>
    <details><summary>Can I call for emergency plumbing or electrical service?</summary><p>Yes. Call 647-980-9211 for urgent issues such as active leaks, sewer backups, burst pipes, sparks, burning smells, power loss, unsafe outlets or repeated breaker trips.</p></details>
    <details><summary>Which plumbing services do you handle?</summary><p>Fateh helps with emergency plumbing, drain cleaning, leak detection, pipe repair, sewer line repair, water heater repair, toilet and faucet repair, sump pump repair, fixture service and commercial plumbing.</p></details>
    <details><summary>Which electrical services do you handle?</summary><p>Fateh helps with emergency electrician calls, electrical repairs, panel upgrades, EV charger installation, lighting installation, wiring, smart home setup, troubleshooting and safety checks.</p></details>
    <details><summary>Do you serve areas outside Brampton?</summary><p>Yes. Fateh is based in Brampton and serves nearby GTA communities when scheduling allows. Call with your location and the service needed so we can help with the right plumbing or electrical service.</p></details>
